{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"662f62e426fc3d176f951baffe5d7d41ae57c0ea76873893c4c0249f4790bd7b","slug":"large-system-with-vibe-coding","location":"/essay/code/large_system_with_vibe_coding.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"在Vibe Coding时代构建大型系统","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/essay/code/large_system_with_vibe_coding.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/essay/code/large_system_with_vibe_coding.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"large_system_with_vibe_coding.md","url":"/large_system_with_vi-03eb38e8927fc4b7b7389313e1042e00.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"引言","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"TU8HrT21JD"}],"identifier":"id","label":"引言","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"sK0OM4VoUL"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们正处在一个编程方式急剧变革的时代。AI生成代码的能力以指数级增长，开发者越来越多地采用“vibe coding”——一种基于直觉和快速反馈的编程方式，让AI承担大量编码工作，人类则负责引导和纠偏。这种模式极大提升了开发效率，但也带来了新的挑战：当AI可以快速产出大量代码时，如何确保系统的长期质量？如何在迭代中避免技术债的累积？当AI犯下根本性错误时，我们该如何应对？","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"rnbx2aMZ5d"}],"key":"wLvVEsEijm"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近，我经历了一次完整的vibe coding协作开发，目标是构建一个嵌入式批注功能模块。整个过程跌宕起伏，AI频频犯错，我频频指正，但每一次纠偏都让系统更健壮，也让AI的“工程直觉”更敏锐。更重要的是，我们从这次经历中提炼出了一套在AI生成环境下构建大型系统的方法论。这篇工作札记，就是这段经历的深度复盘。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"qBKAAMD64C"}],"key":"PBYk3w3qWp"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一、混乱中的秩序：一次协作切片","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"PPNDtBb8a8"}],"identifier":"id","label":"一、混乱中的秩序：一次协作切片","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"I5s3x7yJEm"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一切从一个看似简单的任务开始：为平台准备一个测试样例。我需要AI复制一份工作日志作为输入fixture，并从产品日志中提取“效果演示”部分，生成标准的输出fixture。AI很快完成了复制，但生成输出fixture时，它直接复制了整个产品设计文档——包括前面的需求描述、设计思路，而不仅仅是那段纯日志。更糟的是，它没有使用Markdown引用格式来标记AI批注，而是用了普通段落。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"tuylpyVgFK"}],"key":"yexlgkUME2"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这个小插曲暴露了AI在面对模糊边界时的“漂移”倾向：它不知道哪些是文档、哪些是示例，哪些是内容、哪些是说明。我必须第一时间介入，建立清晰的边界规则：“只取示例部分，不要包含产品设计文档；AI批注必须用引用格式，严格复用用户给的示例。”AI迅速修正，问题得以控制。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"l4HayDMhTW"}],"key":"sIx3ve7ouA"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"但这个教训只是开始。随后在文档编写阶段，AI提交的PRD和DEV文档虽然结构完整，却缺失了关键的实现细节——待定项未填、Prompt未暴露，开发者拿到手根本无法“开箱即用”。我判定为“半成品”，要求整体重写，而不是局部修补。AI重新设计，补充了模块划分、函数职责，甚至画出了伪代码。但它仍然漏掉了文件写入逻辑的一致性、批注标识符的格式、CLI配置的初始化……每一次反馈，都填补一个“想当然”的空缺。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"A6FHcgAeFa"}],"key":"gTAtJy7L03"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代码实现阶段，问题更加典型。AI引入了一个","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"Wce2KtBmcA"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"DefaultConfig","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"ZCxxG0MYdI"},{"type":"text","value":"类和","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"TlAXhATa8l"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"load_default_config","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"a7RuHg3QcW"},{"type":"text","value":"函数，硬编码了opencode路径，还在主入口中保留了冗余代码。这些过度设计让代码库变得臃肿，硬编码则让系统无法在不同环境中运行。我的指令简单直接：“移除”“重写”“删除”。AI立刻执行“大踏步后退”，删除了冗余模块，改用环境变量管理配置，重写了CLI入口。代码库瞬间恢复简洁一致。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"YM3FmVzDc9"}],"key":"eBi7tEh5u3"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下午，我让AI扮演QA专家，对整个仓库进行全面审计。结果令人震惊：没有测试文件，Settings字段缺失，导入没有防护，数据路径指向错误……更严重的是，它发现了未来可用性风险——依赖未声明、版本兼容性问题、构建失败隐患。这些深层次问题在之前的快速迭代中都被忽略了。角色轮换让AI获得了全局视角，提前暴露了隐患。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"NKFcN7ZoYD"}],"key":"BCTUESzGvv"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最后，我要求AI对整个轮次进行系统性复盘。它将经验分为两类：可写成教程/报告/札记的“经验知识”，以及需固化到案例/手册/标准/章程中的“制度规范”。从具体事件到通用原则的跃迁，在这一步完成。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"uXyGn4F2PW"}],"key":"CR4w69YPsG"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"二、从经验到法则：驾驭AI的工程原则","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"W8oX4k6Ike"}],"identifier":"id-ai","label":"二、从经验到法则：驾驭AI的工程原则","html_id":"id-ai","implicit":true,"key":"We0izLkR0x"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这一天的碰撞，让我们提炼出了一套适用于AI快速生成环境下的工程法则。每一个法则都源自真实的纠偏时刻，是应对AI“自由发挥”倾向的利器。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"r4geuWF1E0"}],"key":"jXbzz8IaoO"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. 文档驱动开发的强化版：双向透明与格式锁定","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"On1BWAl1xR"}],"identifier":"id-1","label":"1. 文档驱动开发的强化版：双向透明与格式锁定","html_id":"id-1-1","implicit":true,"key":"I1BANYXTio"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI初版文档遗漏了Prompt和待定项，导致开发者无法理解AI的决策逻辑；样例生成中未复用用户格式，导致样式不一致。因此，我们要求：PRD和DEV文档必须暴露Prompt和所有“待定”项，让AI的思考过程可审查、可追溯。同时，关键标识符（如","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"UmBl7YxB6M"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"🤖 观察者注","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"pOhaJBOWzU"},{"type":"text","value":"）和引用格式一旦确定，就必须永久锁定，防止AI自由发挥引入不一致。这相当于为AI的“创作”划定了一条清晰的格式边界。","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"WtM511xrSw"}],"key":"ivZn1nwA5H"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. 配置中心化与硬编码零容忍","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"CSVYPD0Z82"}],"identifier":"id-2","label":"2. 配置中心化与硬编码零容忍","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"aBJ6jjQE22"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代码实现中，AI硬编码了opencode路径和超时时间，导致系统无法在不同环境中运行；","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"sTDXD25Reu"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"load_default_config","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"OYFeOiZ9JK"},{"type":"text","value":"的过度设计增加了维护负担。因此，我们确立：所有环境敏感项——路径、密钥、超时——都必须通过","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"TR4GKg6a8o"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":".env","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"cmzAgCEcBI"},{"type":"text","value":"文件加Settings类注入，任何硬编码在审查中都会被一票否决。这不仅保证了当前的可移植性，也为未来的配置变更留出了空间。","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"xlzxHgSieW"}],"key":"pG0QSzLdK8"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3. 不可变模块与原子化重构","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"rQDXYnOXMn"}],"identifier":"id-3","label":"3. 不可变模块与原子化重构","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"PfR7vlLGlC"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当发现模块存在系统性缺陷时（如","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"wls4daXLst"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"load_default_config","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"Cu7HiCVPZu"},{"type":"text","value":"），我们不修补，而是整体删除后基于最新规范重写。修补只会累积技术债，而原子化重构能重置系统健康度。保留事件日志作为不可变基线，确保任何一次“后退”都有据可查。","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"ssnADZEogQ"}],"key":"N60wJUVJ40"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4. 测试先行与质量护栏","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"WYHbO0UboH"}],"identifier":"id-4","label":"4. 测试先行与质量护栏","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"i6Hc8GQrMu"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"质量审计中暴露的测试缺失和字段未定义问题，说明测试必须前置，而不是事后补充。因此，Mode层必须配套单元测试，基础导入测试和配置测试必须通过才能合入。将反复出现的检查点自动化，形成预提交钩子，让质量检查成为开发流程的一部分，而非事后救火。","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"key":"gbhCbxwgm9"}],"key":"YbntY224XI"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5. 角色轮换与视角拓展","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"key":"krK9DPDC9f"}],"identifier":"id-5","label":"5. 角色轮换与视角拓展","html_id":"id-5","implicit":true,"key":"yyrIcMWtWS"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"让AI扮演QA后，它发现了之前作为开发者时完全忽略的深层次问题。因此，定期让AI扮演不同角色（设计者、文档员、QA、复盘者），强制从多维度审视系统。每次角色转换后，AI都会自动将新视角的考量融入后续设计——例如，担任QA后，它会在设计时主动考虑测试覆盖和依赖管理。","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"key":"y18eW8EoFm"}],"key":"slBivhTYqA"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三、作为架构导师：我的指导哲学","position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"key":"ufB1NVm2U6"}],"identifier":"id","label":"三、作为架构导师：我的指导哲学","html_id":"id-6","implicit":true,"key":"mZFJAEZD3z"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":49,"column":1},"end":{"line":49,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果说前两部分记录了事件和法则，那么这一部分试图捕捉的，是我在这场协作中的思维特质——那些难以言传但至关重要的指导哲学。","position":{"start":{"line":49,"column":1},"end":{"line":49,"column":1}},"key":"ny5Ya5pHuY"}],"key":"LeCYCyFZkh"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"源头治理者的本能","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"key":"iF1uMPSenB"}],"identifier":"id","label":"源头治理者的本能","html_id":"id-7","implicit":true,"key":"vl3EnG6tE3"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我习惯于在混乱发生前建立秩序。在每个任务开始时，我都会预埋“规范种子”：强制格式统一、预置检查清单、明确边界规则。这种前瞻性来自对AI“自由发挥倾向”的深刻理解——我知道AI会在哪里跑偏，就在哪里提前设障。样例准备中的“格式漂移”事件，正是这一本能的体现：我在问题刚露头时就介入，避免了后续更大范围的蔓延。","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"key":"tJP8xDFvTi"}],"key":"ICnpA97CFx"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"架构师式的决策分层","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"key":"aXEjvxky89"}],"identifier":"id","label":"架构师式的决策分层","html_id":"id-8","implicit":true,"key":"ZQHLPspPnD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我从不亲自设计模块，而是设计一套让AI能自主设计的规则系统。我的审查焦点始终集中在关键质量门上——文档完整性、配置中心化、测试覆盖——而不是代码细节。这样，我就能将精力集中在真正影响系统架构的决策上，而把具体的实现交由AI完成。这是一种“管理设计的设计”，类似于编程中的元编程。","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"key":"dz1nepN2Hq"}],"key":"nVFtmZBYIR"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“大踏步后退”的勇气与智慧","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"em9bK2M9zW"}],"identifier":"id","label":"“大踏步后退”的勇气与智慧","html_id":"id-9","implicit":true,"key":"zC8FsdRJdi"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当发现AI的设计偏离根本原则时，我能果断要求整体重写，即使这意味着丢弃已投入的时间。这种勇气源于对不可变原则的信仰：在错误基础上修补只会累积技术债，而干净的重写能重置系统健康度。删除","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"AZdLqddI7D"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"load_default_config","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"qSbqqntz7W"},{"type":"text","value":"、重写","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"nRBbuPcv0m"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"__main__.py","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"AUB5hIPlwR"},{"type":"text","value":"，都是这种智慧的体现。我的后退不是倒退，而是基于更优基线的跳跃式前进。","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"EUKhydWn3w"}],"key":"DOoqBtDKhB"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"节奏感：收放自如的干预粒度","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"Oyko1sUvs6"}],"identifier":"id","label":"节奏感：收放自如的干预粒度","html_id":"id-10","implicit":true,"key":"EB0hOxcZzf"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我时刻感知着AI的状态，动态调整干预的力度。在AI表现稳定时，我会大幅放权——比如让它独立担任QA、自主复盘；在AI出现系统性偏差时，我会立即收紧，给出极具体的指令——“删除X文件，重写Y函数”。这种节奏使AI始终处于“最近发展区”，既不被放任自流，也不被过度束缚。","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"key":"MxeQbUL6eJ"}],"key":"ZVWqLvOW9y"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"元认知培养者：让AI学会反思","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"key":"T1bJidatrN"}],"identifier":"id-ai","label":"元认知培养者：让AI学会反思","html_id":"id-ai-1","implicit":true,"key":"Y7m1xXHpKb"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":69,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我不仅要求AI完成任务，还强制它进行3E评估和根因分析。每一次错误都被转化为AI认知升级的契机。最终，AI能自主提炼经验并规划制度，这正是长期“教AI如何学习”的结果。我不再只是修正AI的输出，而是在塑造它的思维模式。","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":69,"column":1}},"key":"LowjW2Gug9"}],"key":"NcVNdedGGs"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1},"end":{"line":71,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"结语","position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1},"end":{"line":71,"column":1}},"key":"ELFxdYlBgP"}],"identifier":"id","label":"结语","html_id":"id-11","implicit":true,"key":"UwgiShxIk0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当大多数人在vibe coding中被动接受AI的输出时，我主动构建了一个认知控制系统，让AI的创造力在工程约束内有序释放。我不是AI的助手，而是AI的架构导师。这一天的经历证明，即使在快速迭代的AI时代，构建大型系统依然需要坚实的工程原则和人类的智慧引导。事件记忆提供了事实基础，语义记忆将教训转化为知识，自我记忆锚定了协作关系。三者共同构成了一个可进化的人机协作认知系统——它超越简单的\"提示工程\"，开创了在AI时代构建大型软件的新范式。","position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"key":"Uzmuh7XyMN"}],"key":"BayxO0XTog"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在vibe coding的浪潮中，我们不必随波逐流，而可以成为浪潮的驾驭者。","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"key":"v9LOzeii77"}],"key":"gP1oeGZ2r6"}],"key":"V0FwVcO4Lf"}],"key":"SkEmoMdMJH"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}